name: No shift submissions for today
query:
SELECT fs.name as "Fuel Station:Link/Fuel Station:100",
    fs.cluster_manager as "Cluster Manager:Link/User:150",
    fs.station_manager as "Station Manager:Link/User:150"
  FROM `tabFuel Station` fs
  WHERE fs.name NOT IN (SELECT s.fuel_station FROM `tabShift` s WHERE s.date = CURDATE())
